.
otherwise, when you have eaten and are satisfied, and have built good houses and lived in them, -- deuteronomy 8:12
.
and when your herds and your flocks multiply, and your silver and gold multiply, and all that you have multiplies, -- deuteronomy 8:13
.
then your heart will become proud and you will forget the LORD your God who brought you out from the land of Egypt, out of the house of slavery. -- deuteronomy 8:14
.
