.
Then the second lot fell to Simeon, to the tribe of the sons of Simeon according to their families, and their inheritance was in the midst of the inheritance of the sons of Judah. -- joshua 19:1
.
So they had as their inheritance Beersheba or Sheba and Moladah, -- joshua 19:2
.
and Hazar-shual and Balah and Ezem, -- joshua 19:3
