The sixth lot fell to the sons of Naphtali; to the sons of Naphtali according to their families. -- joshua 19:32
.
Their border was from Heleph, from the oak in Zaanannim and Adami-nekeb and Jabneel, as far as Lakkum, and it ended at the Jordan. -- joshua 19:33
.
